        <text>
          <![CDATA[ <p><strong>No Honor for Treason Act</strong></p> <p>This bill prohibits the provision of military honors at the funeral or burial of any person who has been convicted of a felony committed on January 6, 2021, in or on the U.S. Capitol buildings and grounds.<br> </p>]]>
        </text>
