      <item>
        <titleType>Official Title as Introduced</titleType>
        <title>To amend title 10, United States Code, to prohibit military honors at the funeral, burial, or inurnment of an individual convicted of a felony committed on January 6, 2021, in or on the United States Capitol Buildings and Grounds.</title>
      </item>
